comments: Olynyk (TOR) grabs Lillard's (MIL) right arm and the contact causes him to lose control of the ball.
Lillard (MIL) jumps forwards into Barrett (TOR), dislodging him from his position as he secures the rebound.
Jackson Jr. (MIL) establishes himself in Agbaji's (TOR) path and although he is in a slightly wide position, the contact with Agbaji is marginal as he moves around the screen.
Quickley (TOR) contests Connaughton's (MIL) jump shot and the contact after the release, and follow-through, is marginal.
Olynyk (TOR) establishes screening position in Jackson Jr.'s (MIL) path and marginal body contact occurs as the pick is set.
Jackson Jr. (MIL) wraps his arm around Olynyk (TOR), affecting his FOM as he releases from his screening position.
After communicating with the Replay Center, Portis (MIL) is assessed an unsportsmanlike technical foul as a result of the dead ball contact with Quickley (TOR).
Olynyk (TOR) extends his forearm into Portis's (MIL) back, affecting his ability to secure the rebound.
Portis (MIL) establishes screening position in Trent Jr.'s (TOR) path and marginal contact occurs to his side as the pick is set.
Beasley (MIL) contests the jump shot attempt and avoids making contact with Quickley's (TOR) arm.
Beasley (MIL) and Quickley (TOR) come together in the air after Quickley secures the rebound and he maintains his balance after the resulting contact.
Connaughton (MIL) commits a take foul on Quickley (TOR).
Trent Jr. (TOR) legally contests Green's (MIL) jump shot attempt.
Connaughton (MIL) jumps into Barrett (TOR) after he secures the ball, causing him to lose his balance.
